quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  3,101,"Ni gute mwahakana kandi musomerwa amagambo ya Allah ndetse n’Intumwa ye iri kumwe namwe? Kandi uzashikama ku nzira ya Allah, rwose aba ayobowe inzira igororotse.",""
  3,102,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimungandukire Allah uko bikwiye, kandi ntimuzapfe mutari Abayisilamu (nyakuri).",""
  3,103,"Munafatane urunana mwese ku mugozi wa Allah (Qur’an) kandi ntimugatatane. Munibuke ingabire za Allah yabahundagajeho ubwo bamwe bari abanzi b’abandi, nuko ahuza imitima yanyu maze ku bw’ingabire ze muba abavandimwe. Mwari no ku nkengero z’urwobo rw’umuriro arawubakiza. Uko ni ko Allah abagaragariza ibimenyetso bye kugira ngo muyoboke.",""
  3,104,"Kandi muri mwe habemo itsinda rihamagarira gukora ibyiza, ritegeka ibiboneye rikanabuza ibibi. Rwose abo ni bo bakiranutsi.",""
  3,105,"Ntimuzanabe nka ba bandi batatanye ntibanavuge rumwe nyuma y’uko ibimenyetso bigaragara bibagezeho. Abo bazahanishwa ibihano bihambaye.",""
  3,106,"Ku munsi (w’imperuka) uburanga buzererana ubundi bwijime; abo uburanga bwabo buzaba bwijimye (bazabwirwa) bati “Ese mwahakanye nyuma y’uko mwemeye? Ngaho nimusogongere ububabare bw’ibihano kubera ubuhakanyi bwanyu.”",""
  3,107,"Naho abo uburanga bwabo buzaba bwererana, bazaba mu mpuhwe za Allah, bazazibemo ubuziraherezo.",""
  3,108,"Ayo ni amagambo ya Allah tugusomera mu kuri (yewe Muhamadi), kandi Allah ntajya ahuguza ibiremwa.",""
